text: Ulla Werner Hansen (born 27 November 1973) is a Danish rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Denmark Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
